it to Hell Fest with Quinn (Christian James), Brooke's boyfriend, Taylor's boyfriend Asher (Matt Mercurio), and their respective friend Gavin (Roby Attal) who is attracted to Natalie..</p>","tmdb_id":429476,"cast":["Amy Forsyth","Christian James","Reign Edwards","Roby Attal","Bex Taylor-Klaus","Matt Mercurio","Courtney Dietz","Cynthea Mercado","Stephen Conroy","George Howard Adams","Markus Silbiger","Michael Tourek","Tony Todd","Aaron Gillespie","Cecil Elmore Jr."],"director":["Gregory Plotkin"],"keywords":["psychopath","halloween","serial killer","slasher","amusement park","psycho","halloween night"],"tmdb":{"type":"movie","id":"429476","season":null,"vote_average":5.682,"vote_count":869},"cast_meta":[{"name":"Amy Forsyth","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Amy Forsyth","tmdb_id":1369336,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ii3DqSprC4MTFsqzjAloynqVOKB.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1369336"},{"name":"Christian James","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Christian James","tmdb_id":2021815,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/I3iUTkICSDBnk08uYGljCd1uFx.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2021815"},{"name":"Reign Edwards","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Reign Edwards","tmdb_id":1978175,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6dprqMjxCzAVWi3ujqnvq3d5vgO.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1978175"},{"name":"Roby Attal","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Roby Attal","tmdb_id":2092072,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/16BjgAcczlVNmGVFXAqZVbpPo4z.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2092072"},{"name":"Bex Taylor-Klaus","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Bex Taylor-Klaus","tmdb_id":1252871,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gX0uZhSO31wUPM2rRAg09XK0Zjv.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1252871"},{"name":"Matt Mercurio","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Matt Mercurio","tmdb_id":1705851,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/GgvUolaiAFTnTxj6YnbSFPT45b.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://